parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "SURFEX",
  "software": [
    "MASTERODB",
    "openmpi",
    "grib_api",
    "eccodes",
    "rttov12"
  ],
  "resource": [
    "2 cores",
    "20 GB RAM",
    "10 minutes runtime",
    "normal256 partition",
    "export variables: MYLIB, HOME, HOMEPACK, TMPDIR, OUTPUTDIR, TESTDIR",
    "OMP_NUM_THREADS=1",
    "DR_HOOK=1",
    "DR_HOOK_NOT_MPI=1",
    "DR_HOOK_SILENT=1",
    "EC_PROFILE_HEAP=0",
    "EC_PROFILE_MEM=0",
    "EC_MPI_ATEXIT=0",
    "DR_HOOK_SHOW_PROCESS_OPTIONS=0",
    "EC_MEMINFO=0",
    "RTTOV_COEFDIR=$PWD",
    "HOMEPACK=${HOMEPACK:=$HOME/pack}",
    "SOURCE=$HOMEPACK/$MYLIB/src/local",
    "LOADIR=$HOMEPACK/$MYLIB/bin",
    "TMPDIR=${TMPDIR:=$HOME/tmp}",
    "TMPLOC=$TMPDIR/rundir.$$",
    "TMPWAIT=$TMPDIR/wait_queue.$$"
  ]
}
```
